    <abstract id="aspace_b5eee2dc4cc3cc056ec9a113767225d9">This collection contains correspondence, deeds, indentures, wills, land conveyances, genealogies, and printed materials from the 17th through 19th centuries. The majority of the collection relates to New York and the surrounding states, but some items are from New England or the Mid-Atlantic region. Materials are in English, French, and Dutch. Subjects of note include Native American relations and slavery.</abstract>
    <langmaterial id="aspace_98c6fc97f1333d9c9a4c7735d1c50a27">Materials are primarily in English, with some additional materials in Dutch and French.</langmaterial>
